trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Sendt til egendefinert WSDL eksportverktøy og import aktiverer tilpassing av metadata eksporten og importerer prosesser for et WSDL-endepunkt.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WsdlEndpointConversionContext representerer konteksten der egendefinerte WSDL for et endepunkt er enten eksporteres ved hjelp av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>eller importert ved hjelp av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: Følgende egenskaper gjør det mulig å hente WSDL dokumentobjektmodellen for gjeldende WSDL: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>egenskapen henter den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>for endepunktet kontrakten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>Egenskapen henter den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName>for gjeldende sluttpunktet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>Egenskapen henter bindingen for gjeldende endepunktet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>Egenskapen henter porten for gjeldende endepunktet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>

trans-unit.source: - - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: --Følgende metoder gjør det mulig å legge til eller fjerne egendefinerte WSDL-elementer til de riktige omfangene i eksporterte eller importerte WSDL: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>metoden returnerer feil bindingen for den angitte feilen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>Metoden returnerer feilen for den angitte feil bindingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>Metoden returnerer meldingen bindingen for den angitte meldingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>Metoden returnerer meldingen for den angitte bindingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>Metoden returnerer operasjonen bindingen for den angitte operasjonen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>Metoden returnerer operasjonen for den angitte operasjon bindingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>
